*pypcap-1.1.3 (06 Jun 2015)

  06 Jun 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +pypcap-1.1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  03 Jun 2015; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add pypi to remote-id in metadata.xml

  16 Jan 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -pypcap-1.1-r1.ebuild,
  -pypcap-1.1-r2.ebuild, pypcap-1.1.1.ebuild, -files/include_path.patch:
  Fix DEPEND.

*pypcap-1.1.1 (12 Aug 2014)

  12 Aug 2014; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org> +pypcap-1.1.1.ebuild:
  bump, add pypy support, fixes Bug #519326

*pypcap-1.1-r2 (11 Aug 2014)

  11 Aug 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +pypcap-1.1-r2.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Migrate to distutils-r1. EAPI bump. Install single small example file
  unconditionally. Install README. Add netmon herd.

  02 Apr 2012; Naohiro Aota <naota@gentoo.org> pypcap-1.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd

  22 Feb 2012; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> pypcap-1.1-r1.ebuild:
  Restricting jython

  08 Jan 2012; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> pypcap-1.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fix building with net-libs/libpcap[-static-libs] (bug #397647). Patch by
  Arfrever

  02 Apr 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> pypcap-1.1-r1.ebuild:
  Use net-libs/libpcap instead of virtual/libpcap wrt #358835.

  08 Jul 2010; Arfrever Frehtes Taifersar Arahesis <arfrever@gentoo.org>
